    <H1>Skin Look and Feel Decorator</H1><DIV class="s1">
      <P>A theme for Skin look and feel</P>
      <IMG alt="skin01" class="figure" src="images/skin01.gif">
      <P>Another</P>
      <IMG alt="skin02" class="figure" src="images/skin02.gif">
      <P>Another</P>
      <IMG alt="skin03" class="figure" src="images/skin03.gif">
      <P>
	The Skin Look and Feel for Swing has been adapted to become a pluggable decorator.  The control panel for the decorator allows a number of configurations for appearance.  These are the skins that are listed on the main Skin Look and Feel site - mac, windows, beos, mozilla.
      </P>
      <P>
        There is still plenty to do for Oyoaha:
      </P>
      <OL>
        <LI>Use Radio buttons in the configration tool, rather than check boxes</LI>
        <LI>Allow loadable themepack files.</LI>
      </OL>
    </DIV>
